I was on a certain...Other website, looking for ASMR, because the top triggers that give me serious tingles are mouth sounds and direct kissing, and those just don't really happen as much on youtube. Then I checked my subs and saw Gibi holding some toast, closed out of that "other" place, and am back here safe and sound on youtube, going to sleep to the smooth sounds of toast tapping. Tapping is easily my 2nd highest trigger in terms of tingles, and certain types of tapping or objects even surpass kissing/mouth sounds.


This toast is one of them.
